name: Technology
description: Technological products like laptops, desktops, servers, etc.

name: Land (not built)
description: Purchases of land without buildings

name: Buildings
description: Construction of buildings and costs associated to buildings

name: Improvements
description: Purchases of installations related to buildings, like solar panels or HVAC

name: Machines & Tools
description: Equipment, machinery and tools directly related to your business

name: Other property
description: Other type of property, like plants, machinery or various equipment

name: Furniture & Fixtures
description: Office desks, chairs, shelving, etc

name: Vehicles
description: Purchase of a car or truck, including second hand or after-lease contract

name: Accumulated Amortization - Technology
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for capitalized technology assets.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Buildings
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for building assets.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Improvements
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for leasehold or property improvements.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Machines & Tools
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for machinery and tool assets.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Other Property
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for other depreciable property assets.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Furniture & Fixtures
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for furniture and fixture assets.

name: Accumulated Amortization - Vehicles
description: Cumulative amortization recorded for vehicle assets.

name: Raw Materials
description: All goods purchased as raw materials used by your activity

name: Salaries & Wages
description: Compensation paid to employees and workers employed by the company

name: Employees Commissions
description: Employees commissions and bonuses

name: Pension
description: Retirement plans costs (401K match)

name: Healthcare Benefits
description: Employees medical, dental, and vision benefits

name: Workers Compensation Insurance
description: Insurance premiums that cover medical costs and wage replacement for employees injured on the job

name: Payroll Tax
description: Employer's portion of payroll-related taxes (eg. Social Security, Medicare, FUTA/SUTA)

name: Other Employees Benefits
description: Company's personnel costs excluding compensations, contributions and vouchers

name: Social Security
description: All fees related to social security contributions

name: Accounting
description: Bills from your bookkeeper or accounting firm

name: Legal
description: Bills from lawyers, fees paid to the justice system

name: General Subcontracting
description: Compensation to external workers and consultants for services

name: Administration Fees
description: Services incurred for the administration of your business (excluding supplies)

name: Dues & Subscriptions
description: Membership fees for industry groups, professional associations, etc

name: Office Rent
description: Rent or lease of buildings

name: Telephone & Internet
description: Phone and internet bills from your telco provider for business operations

name: Utilities
description: Utility bills for water, gas, electricity, heating, etc

name: Disposal Fees
description: Costs incurred for removal, disposal, or recycling of waste and obsolete materials

name: Bank Fees
description: Nasty charges and interests from your bank

name: Office Maintenance
description: Services related to the maintenance of your worplace, like repair or janitorial

name: Office Supplies
description: Various supplies bought for your workplace or office, like pencils, paper, consumables, etc

name: Postage and Delivery
description: Costs for shipping products or materials to customers or receiving inventory.

name: Printing and Reproduction
description: Production of printed or digital materials, such as photocopies, brochures, flyers, manuals.

name: Equipment and Furniture
description: Cost of office furniture, fixtures, and business equipment

name: Computers
description: Expenses made for the repair and maintenance of laptops, peripherals, and computing equipment

name: Office Services
description: All expenses made for your office or workplace that are not material goods

name: Software
description: Licenses or computer services (like repairs or upgrades)

name: Professional Liability Insurance
description: Insurance for damage caused to third parties

name: Unemployment Insurance
description: Employer contributions to state (SUI) or federal unemployment insurance programs

name: Disability Insurance
description: Premiums for short-term or long-term disability coverage provided to employees

name: Professional Insurance
description: All fees related to insurance taken in the context of your business

name: Licenses and Permits
description: Business licenses and permits that your company must pay to operate

name: Ground Transportation
description: Mileage, taxi and parking

name: Public Transportation
description: Travel expenses done using public transit (metro, bus, tramways, ...)

name: Airfare
description: Flights or expenses related to air travel by plane

name: Hotels
description: Hotel or accommodation expenses incurred during business trips

name: Vehicles
description: Expenses made for the repair and maintenance of company cars and trucks

name: Vehicle Rent
description: Rental of cars or trucks, including shared services, but excluding leasing

name: Fuel
description: All fuel and gas expenses for a car/auto

name: Auto Insurance
description: Premiums paid for insurance coverage on company-owned or leased vehicles

name: Meals & Entertainment
description: Expenses incurred when eating or drinking at bars or restaurants

name: Food: Catering & Delivery
description: Food or drinks incurred outside of bars or restaurants, like receptions, canteen and food delivery, etc

name: Advertising & Marketing
description: Costs related to promoting the business, such as ads, campaigns, etc

name: Depreciation Expense - Technology
description: Periodic depreciation expense for capitalized technology assets.

name: Depreciation Expense - Buildings
description: Periodic depreciation expense for building assets.

name: Depreciation Expense - Improvements
description: Periodic depreciation expense for leasehold or property improvements.

name: Depreciation Expense - Machines & Tools
description: Periodic depreciation expense for machinery and tool assets.

name: Depreciation Expense - Other Property
description: Periodic depreciation expense for other depreciable property assets.

name: Depreciation Expense - Furniture & Fixtures
description: Periodic depreciation expense for furniture and fixture assets.

name: Depreciation Expense - Vehicles
description: Periodic depreciation expense for vehicle assets.

name: Training and Documentation
description: Education and training fees not including food and drinks

name: Miscellaneous Expenses
description: All other uncategorized expenses

name: Loan Interest Expense
description: Interest paid on loans or lines of credit

name: Import Fees
description: Customs fees incurred while importing goods from outside of the US

name: Federal Income Tax
description: Income taxes owed to the U.S. federal government

name: State Income Tax
description: Income taxes owed to state taxing authorities

name: Local/City Tax
description: Business or income taxes owed to local or municipal governments

name: Property Tax
description: Local taxes that have to be paid due to the ownership of property

name: Sales Tax
description: Sales and use tax paid on purchases where not otherwise recoverable
